Theme: MongoDB Cluster

Target: File Structure on Standalone servers

On WiredTiger, the default journal commit interval is 100 milliseconds.

Lecture Instructions

List --dbpath directory:

ls -l /data/db

List diagnostics data directory:

ls -l /data/db/diagnostic.data

List journal directory:

ls -l /data/db/journal

List socket file:

ls /tmp/mongodb-27017.sock

